        <type>void</type>
        <definition>void XDpDc_GenerateFrameInfoAttribute</definition>
        <argsstring>(FrameInfo *Frame)</argsstring>
        <name>XDpDc_GenerateFrameInfoAttribute</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="struct_frame_info" kindref="compound">FrameInfo</ref> *</type>
          <declname>Frame</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This function computes the frame buffer Size, LineSize, and Stride attributes from the Width, Height, and Bpc fields of a <ref refid="struct_frame_info" kindref="compound">FrameInfo</ref> structure. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Stride is aligned to a 256-byte boundary.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Frame</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_frame_info" kindref="compound">FrameInfo</ref> structure to populate.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
