        <briefdescription>
<para>This function initializes a DMA descriptor with source address, data size, line size, stride, and next descriptor linkage from the given <ref refid="struct_frame_info" kindref="compound">FrameInfo</ref>. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For cursor descriptors, Target_Addr is also set.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>RunCfgPtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the application configuration structure. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>XDesc</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the DMA descriptor to initialize. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>FBInfo</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_frame_info" kindref="compound">FrameInfo</ref> containing buffer attributes. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>NextDesc</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the next descriptor in the chain, <verbatim>    or NULL for a self-linked (last) descriptor.
</verbatim></para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
