        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This function initializes video, cursor, and audio frame buffers. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Buffer initialization is format-aware: the number of planes per stream is</para><para>determined by the video format mode (Interleaved/SemiPlanar/Planar). V1-V3 are Stream1 planes, V4-V6 are Stream2 planes.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
