</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the application configuration structure.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Descriptor creation is handled separately by XDpDc_SetupStream1Descriptors and XDpDc_SetupStream2Descriptors, which must be called after DMA hardware initialization. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
